- client -> api_gateway (AGW) -> business_logic/service
- usual functions:
transparent proxy (HTTP-X_Forwarde for to see not only local IP)
web application firewall (request analysis for security issues in requests)
quotes (limiting amout of requests to service/delaying incomnig requests => service hopefully will no fail)
tracing (for debug)
routing&balancing
service_discovery (control of services and infrastructure)
authorization (to avoid on service level)
logging (analitics, statistics, debugging, monitoring)
protocols
...
